   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1893_AS_RBH_1_00039"/><hi rend="latintype">Herrn Doctor Richard</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Beer Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb190427" type="place">I Wollzeile 15</rs></hi>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="1893_AS_RBH_1_00040"/>Lieber Richard,</salute></opener><p>der kleine <rs ref="#pmb11988" type="person">Kraus</rs> wird Ihnen für
                  <date>Sam<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>Abend</time> einen Sitz zu den <rs ref="#pmb31431" type="work">Räubern</rs> in
                  <rs type="place" ref="#pmb39" subtype="implied"><hi rend="latintype">Rdlfsheim</hi></rs> (<rs type="work" ref="#pmb31431" subtype="implied">Franz Moor</rs> – Herr <rs ref="#pmb11988" type="person">Kraus</rs>)<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>enden.</p><p>Bitte gehen Sie, wir gehen alle. Sollt ich Sie nicht früher<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehen,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o wollen wir uns
               vielleicht im <rs ref="#pmb34" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Griensteidl</hi></rs> um <time>6 Uhr Abds</time> treffen.</p><closer>Herzlich<lb/>Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
